4. DEMO STRATEGY
================

Demo Principles:
1. NEVER demo without discovery first
2. Customize every demo to their specific pain points
3. Show 3 features max - depth over breadth
4. End every demo with clear next steps

Standard Demo Flow (45 minutes):
- Recap pain points (5 min)
- Tailored feature demonstration (25 min)
- Customer questions (10 min)
- Next steps (5 min)

Demo Environments:
- Production demo: demo.velocityrm.io (for most demos)
- Industry-specific: demo-manufacturing.velocityrm.io, demo-finserv.velocityrm.io
- Sandbox: Request via #demo-support in Slack

See Demo/ folder for detailed scripts and gotchas.

