5. PROPOSAL & NEGOTIATION
=========================

Proposal Best Practices:
- Always present proposals live (never just email)
- Include 3 options when possible (good/better/best)
- Lead with business value, not features
- Include clear timeline and next steps

Negotiation Guidelines:
- Never discount without getting something in return
- Common trade items: Contract length, payment terms, case study rights
- Maximum discounts: See pricing documentation
- Always involve manager for discounts >15%

